SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776161176
OL,3,CWhat are Henry VIII powers and why
OL,4,Cmight Keir Starmer use them?
OL,6,FStarmer added that the legislation
OL,7,Fwill make trade easier, reducing
OL,8,F"burdens" on businesses and lowering
OL,9,Fprices.
OL,11,F"A stronger, closer relationship with
OL,12,FEurope is in the UK's best interest,
OL,13,Fparticularly in a world that is as
OL,14,Fvolatile as it is at the moment, and I
OL,15,Fknow that worries a lot of people," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FA government spokesman said: "The Bill
OL,19,Fwill go through parliament in the
OL,20,Fnormal way.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@IO]sD@AOUwD@cO]zD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776161176
OL,3,CWhat are Henry VIII powers and why
OL,4,Cmight Keir Starmer use them?
OL,6,F"Any new treaties or deals with the EU
OL,7,Fwill also face parliamentary scrutiny,
OL,8,Fand parliament will have a role in
OL,9,Fapproving new EU laws required under
OL,10,Fthose deals via secondary legislation."
OL,12,FHave Henry VIII powers been used
OL,13,Fbefore?
OL,15,FConcerns have been previously raised
OL,16,Fin Parliament over the use of Henry
OL,17,FVIII powers in relation to Brexit.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
