OL,3,CWhat are Henry VIII powers and why
OL,4,Cmight Keir Starmer use them?
OL,6,FIn 2017, close to the start of the
OL,7,FUK's withdrawal process from the
OL,8,FEuropean Union, the then-Conservative
OL,9,Fgovernment pushed legislation seeking
OL,10,Fto transpose EU rules and regulations
OL,11,Finto the domestic law books ahead of
OL,12,FBrexit.
OL,14,FThe "Great Repeal Bill" proposed using
OL,15,FHenry VIII powers to allow ministers
OL,16,Fto amend or repeal the regulations
OL,17,Fwhile bypassing full parliamentary
OL,18,Fscrutiny - a move which raised
OL,19,Fsignifican constitutional concerns at
OL,20,Fthe time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776161176
OL,3,CWhat are Henry VIII powers and why
OL,4,Cmight Keir Starmer use them?
OL,6,FThis bill passed the first vote, with
OL,7,FLabour at the time describing it as
OL,8,F"deeply disappointing", the Liberal
OL,9,FDemocrats described it as "a dark day
OL,10,Ffor the mother of parliaments".
OL,12,FNotably, the then-shadow Brexit
OL,13,Fminister, and now prime minister, Sir
OL,14,FKeir Starmer labelled it a "flawed
OL,15,FBill" that should have been "dropped".
OL,17,FHe went on to add it "will need
OL,18,Fextensive amendment and improvement in
OL,19,Fa whole range of areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776161176
OL,3,CWhat are Henry VIII powers and why
OL,4,Cmight Keir Starmer use them?
OL,6,F"Labour amendments would give greater
OL,7,Fcontrol to Parliament and take power
OL,8,Fback from the hands of ministers. They
OL,9,Fwould protect key rights and
OL,10,Fenvironmental safeguards and ensure
OL,11,Fthat the government does not have a
OL,12,Flegislative blank cheque," he said.
OL,14,FThe use of Henry VIII powers is
OL,15,Frelatively rare, but have been used on
OL,16,Fother occasions. One such was during
OL,17,Fthe Childcare Act (2016), which
OL,18,Fdoubled childcare allowance for some
OL,19,Fworking parents. The us of the powers
OL,20,Fhere, too, faced criticism from MPs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
