OL,3,CWhat are Henry VIII powers and why
OL,4,Cmight Keir Starmer use them?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWhy are they so controversial?
OL,13,FCritics of the powers argue that they
OL,14,Freduce the sovereignty and control the
OL,15,FUK has over its own laws, forcing us
OL,16,Fto conform to those of the EU.
OL,18,FConservative Shadow Business Secretary
OL,19,FAndrew Griffith said it would mean
OL,20,FParliament is "reduced to a spectator
OL,21,Fwhile Brussels sets the terms".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
