PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776161176
OL,3,CWhat are Henry VIII powers and why
OL,4,Cmight Keir Starmer use them?
OL,6,FReform UK leader and ardent Brexit
OL,7,Fsupporter Nigel Farage has also
OL,8,Fcriticised the proposals. Saying on
OL,9,FMonday he would fight them "every step
OL,10,Fof the way", branding them "a backdoor
OL,11,Fattempt to drag Britain back under
OL,12,FEuropean Union control".
OL,14,FResponding to the government's plans,
OL,15,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,16,Faccused Starmer of asking the European
OL,17,FUnion to "do his homework" with his
OL,18,Fplans for an EU reset, saying: "It
OL,19,Fworries me that what Starmer is
OL,20,Fplanning looks like the worst of both
OL,21,Fworlds.
OL,26,@yD@JOUyD@ZO]zD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
