PN,31716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776161176
OL,3,CWhat are Henry VIII powers and why
OL,4,Cmight Keir Starmer use them?
OL,6,F"If you're in the EU, you can veto
OL,7,Fplans that you don't like, if you're
OL,8,Fout of the EU, you can create your own
OL,9,Fplans, but simply accepting whatever
OL,10,Fit is that the EU is doing and rubber
OL,11,Fstamping it is a huge concern.
OL,13,F"We need our Parliament to be able to
OL,14,Fmake the laws that are right for this
OL,15,Fcountry rather than just copying what
OL,16,Fthe EU is doing, as doing that makes
OL,17,Fme worry that Starmer hasn't got any
OL,18,Fideas for the future, and is just
OL,19,Fasking for help from the EU and asking
OL,20,Fthem to do his homework."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
