OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776161176
OL,3,CWhat are Henry VIII powers and why
OL,4,Cmight Keir Starmer use them?
OL,6,FAddressing this, one Labour source
OL,7,Fsaid: "We're making a sovereign choice
OL,8,Fto agree deals to reduce trade
OL,9,Fbarriers - where parliament gets to
OL,10,Fhave a say. It will lower costs for
OL,11,Fbusinesses and get rid of the Brexit
OL,12,Fpaperwork tax that adds to the cost of
OL,13,Fthe weekly shop.
OL,15,F"Reform and the Tories are stuck with
OL,16,Fthe ghost of Brexit past, happy with
OL,17,Fthe broken status quo. But in a world
OL,18,Fof rising global tensions, we need
OL,19,Fpoliticians who can build bridges
OL,20,Frather than burn them."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
